{"number":3,"verseCount":20,"verses":[[1,["The ",["works",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG God, Works of","tg/god-works-of"],"."]]],", and the designs, and the purposes of God cannot be ",["frustrated",["study-note-ref","b",[["Jer. 1:8 (7–8)","ot/jer/1.8"],"."]]],", neither can they come to naught."]],[2,["For God doth not ",["walk",["study-note-ref","a",[["Neh. 9:8","ot/neh/9.8"],"; ",["Isa. 45:19","ot/isa/45.19"],"; ",["Alma 7:20","bofm/alma/7.20"],". ",["TG God, Perfection of","tg/god-perfection-of"],"."]]]," in crooked paths, neither doth he ",["turn",["study-note-ref","b",[["Josh. 1:7","ot/josh/1.7"],"; ",["3 Ne. 18:13 (12–14)","bofm/3-ne/18.13"],"."]]]," to the right hand nor to the left, neither doth he vary from that which he hath said, therefore his paths are straight, and his ",["course",["study-note-ref","c",[["1 Ne. 10:19 (18–19)","bofm/1-ne/10.19"],"; ",["D&C 35:1","dc-testament/dc/35.1"],"."]]]," is one eternal round."]],[3,["Remember, remember that it is not the ",["work",["study-note-ref","a",[["Acts 5:38","nt/acts/5.38"],"; ",["Morm. 8:22","bofm/morm/8.22"],"; ",["D&C 10:38 (38–40)","dc-testament/dc/10.38"],"."]]]," of God that is frustrated, but the work of men;"]],[4,["For although a man may have many ",["revelations",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Revelation","tg/revelation"],"."]]],", and have ",["power",["study-note-ref","b",[["Alma 19:4","bofm/alma/19.4"],"."]]]," to do many mighty works, yet if he ",["boasts",["study-note-ref","c",[["Amos 6:13 (13–14)","ot/amos/6.13"],"; ",["Mosiah 11:19","bofm/mosiah/11.19"],"; ",["D&C 84:73","dc-testament/dc/84.73"],". ",["TG Boast","tg/boast"],"."]]]," in his own ",["strength",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Strength","tg/strength"],"."]]],", and sets at naught the ",["counsels",["study-note-ref","e",[["Josh. 9:14","ot/josh/9.14"],"; ",["Jacob 4:10","bofm/jacob/4.10"],"; ",["Alma 37:37","bofm/alma/37.37"],". ",["TG Counsel","tg/counsel"],"."]]]," of God, and follows after the dictates of his own will and ",["carnal",["study-note-ref","f",[["TG Carnal Mind","tg/carnal-mind"],"; ",["Chastity","tg/chastity"],"; ",["Lust","tg/lust"],"."]]]," desires, he must fall and incur the ",["vengeance",["study-note-ref","g",[["TG Vengeance","tg/vengeance"],"."]]]," of a ",["just",["study-note-ref","h",[["2 Ne. 1:22","bofm/2-ne/1.22"],"."]]]," God upon him."]],[5,["Behold, you have been ",["entrusted",["study-note-ref","a",[["Alma 37:14","bofm/alma/37.14"],"."]]]," with these things, but how strict were your commandments; and remember also the promises which were made to you, if you did not transgress them."]],[6,["And behold, how ",["oft",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 5:21","dc-testament/dc/5.21"],"; ",["20:5","dc-testament/dc/20.5"],"; ",["JS—H 1:28 (28–29)","pgp/js-h/1.28"],"."]]]," you have ",["",6],["transgressed",["study-note-ref","b",[["Josh. 23:16 (15–16)","ot/josh/23.16"],"; ",["Alma 12:31","bofm/alma/12.31"],". ",["TG Transgress","tg/transgress"],"."]]]," the commandments and the laws of God, and have gone on in the ",["persuasions",["study-note-ref","c",[["Titus 1:14","nt/titus/1.14"],"; ",["D&C 45:29","dc-testament/dc/45.29"],"; ",["46:7","dc-testament/dc/46.7"],"; ",["JS—H 1:19","pgp/js-h/1.19"],". ",["TG Motivations","tg/motivations"],"; ",["Peer Influence","tg/peer-influence"],"."]]]," of men."]],[7,["For, behold, you should not have ",["feared",["study-note-ref","a",[["Neh. 6:13","ot/neh/6.13"],"; ",["Ps. 27:1 (1–14)","ot/ps/27.1"],"; ",["Isa. 57:11","ot/isa/57.11"],"; ",["Luke 9:26","nt/luke/9.26"],"; ",["John 12:43 (42–43)","nt/john/12.43"],"; ",["Acts 4:19","nt/acts/4.19"],"; ",["D&C 122:9 (4–9)","dc-testament/dc/122.9"],". ",["TG Courage","tg/courage"],"; ",["Fearful","tg/fearful"],"."]]]," man more than God. Although men set at naught the counsels of God, and ",["despise",["study-note-ref","b",[["Num. 15:31 (30–31)","ot/num/15.31"],"; ",["2 Sam. 12:9 (7–9)","ot/2-sam/12.9"],"; ",["1 Ne. 19:7","bofm/1-ne/19.7"],"; ",["2 Ne. 33:2","bofm/2-ne/33.2"],"; ",["Jacob 4:14 (8–14)","bofm/jacob/4.14"],". ",["TG Hate","tg/hate"],"."]]]," his words—"]],[8,["Yet you should have been faithful; and he would have extended his arm and ",["supported",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG God, Power of","tg/god-power-of"],"."]]]," you against all the fiery ",["darts",["study-note-ref","b",[["Eph. 6:16","nt/eph/6.16"],"; ",["1 Ne. 15:24","bofm/1-ne/15.24"],"; ",["D&C 27:17","dc-testament/dc/27.17"],"."]]]," of the ",["adversary",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Devil","tg/devil"],"."]]],"; and he would have been with you in every time of ",["trouble",["study-note-ref","d",[["Ps. 81:7","ot/ps/81.7"],"; ",["Alma 9:17","bofm/alma/9.17"],"; ",["38:5","bofm/alma/38.5"],"."]]],"."]],[9,["Behold, thou art Joseph, and thou wast chosen to do the work of the Lord, but because of transgression, if thou art not aware thou wilt ",["fall",["study-note-ref","a",[["Acts 1:25","nt/acts/1.25"],"; ",["1 Cor. 10:12","nt/1-cor/10.12"],". ",["TG Apostasy of Individuals","tg/apostasy-of-individuals"],"."]]],"."]],[10,["But remember, God is merciful; therefore, repent of that which thou hast done which is contrary to the commandment which I gave you, and thou art still chosen, and art ",["again",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 10:3","dc-testament/dc/10.3"],"."]]]," called to the work;"]],[11,["Except thou ",["do",["study-note-ref","a",[["Luke 13:3","nt/luke/13.3"],"; ",["D&C 1:33","dc-testament/dc/1.33"],"; ",["121:37 (34–37)","dc-testament/dc/121.37"],"."]]]," this, thou shalt be delivered up and become as other men, and have no more gift."]],[12,["And when thou deliveredst up that which God had given thee sight and power to ",["translate",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 1:29","dc-testament/dc/1.29"],"; ",["5:4 (4, 30–31)","dc-testament/dc/5.4"],"."]]],", thou deliveredst up that which was ",["sacred",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Sacred","tg/sacred"],"; ",["Sacrilege","tg/sacrilege"],"."]]]," into the hands of a wicked ",["man",["study-note-ref","c",[["D&C 10:6 (6–8)","dc-testament/dc/10.6"],"."]]],","]],[13,["Who has set at naught the counsels of God, and has broken the most sacred promises which were made before God, and has depended upon his own judgment and ",["boasted",["study-note-ref","a",[["Jacob 4:10","bofm/jacob/4.10"],". ",["TG Haughtiness","tg/haughtiness"],"; ",["Pride","tg/pride"],"."]]]," in his own wisdom."]],[14,["And this is the reason that thou hast lost thy privileges for a season—"]],[15,["For thou hast suffered the counsel of thy ",["director",["study-note-ref","a",["IE the Lord; see ",["v. 6","dc-testament/dc/3.6"],"."]]]," to be trampled upon from the beginning."]],[16,["Nevertheless, my ",["work",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Israel, Mission of","tg/israel-mission-of"],"."]]]," shall go forth, for inasmuch as the knowledge of a Savior has come unto the world, through the ",["testimony",["study-note-ref","b",[["John 5:39","nt/john/5.39"],"; ",["1 Ne. 13:25 (23–25)","bofm/1-ne/13.25"],"; ",["2 Ne. 29:4 (4–6)","bofm/2-ne/29.4"],"; ",["D&C 20:26","dc-testament/dc/20.26"],"."]]]," of the Jews, even so shall the ",["knowledge",["study-note-ref","c",[["Mosiah 3:20","bofm/mosiah/3.20"],"."]]]," of a ",["Savior",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Jesus Christ, Savior","tg/jesus-christ-savior"],"."]]]," come unto my people—"]],[17,["And to the ",["Nephites",["study-note-ref","a",[["1 Ne. 13:30","bofm/1-ne/13.30"],"; ",["2 Ne. 29:12 (12–13)","bofm/2-ne/29.12"],"; ",["Alma 45:14 (10–14)","bofm/alma/45.14"],"."]]],", and the Jacobites, and the Josephites, and the Zoramites, through the testimony of their fathers—"]],[18,["And this ",["testimony",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Testimony","tg/testimony"],"."]]]," shall come to the knowledge of the ",["Lamanites",["study-note-ref","b",[["Jacob 1:13","bofm/jacob/1.13"],"; ",["Enos 1:13","bofm/enos/1.13"],"; ",["D&C 10:48 (46–52)","dc-testament/dc/10.48"],"; ",["109:65","dc-testament/dc/109.65"],"."]]],", and the Lemuelites, and the Ishmaelites, who ",["dwindled",["study-note-ref","c",[["2 Ne. 26:15","bofm/2-ne/26.15"],"; ",["Jacob 3:7","bofm/jacob/3.7"],". ",["TG Doubt","tg/doubt"],"."]]]," in unbelief because of the ",["iniquity",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Family, Children, Responsibilities toward","tg/family-children-responsibilities-toward"],"; ",["Sin","tg/sin"],"."]]]," of their fathers, whom the Lord has suffered to destroy their ",["brethren",["study-note-ref","e",[["Morm. 8:2 (2–3)","bofm/morm/8.2"],"."]]]," the Nephites, because of their ",["iniquities",["study-note-ref","f",[["Mosiah 12:7","bofm/mosiah/12.7"],"."]]]," and their abominations."]],[19,["And for this very ",["purpose",["study-note-ref","a",[["1 Ne. 9:3 (3, 5)","bofm/1-ne/9.3"],"."]]]," are these ",["plates",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Book of Mormon","tg/book-of-mormon"],"."]]]," ",["preserved",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Scriptures, Preservation of","tg/scriptures-preservation-of"],"."]]],", which contain these records—that the ",["promises",["study-note-ref","d",[["Enos 1:16 (13–18)","bofm/enos/1.16"],"; ",["Mosiah 21:4","bofm/mosiah/21.4"],"; ",["3 Ne. 5:14 (13–15)","bofm/3-ne/5.14"],"; ",["D&C 10:47 (46–50)","dc-testament/dc/10.47"],"."]]]," of the Lord might be fulfilled, which he made to his ",["people",["study-note-ref","e",[["TG Israel, Joseph, People of","tg/israel-joseph-people-of"],"; ",["Israel, Restoration of","tg/israel-restoration-of"],"."]]],";"]],[20,["And that the ",["Lamanites",["study-note-ref","a",[["2 Ne. 30:5 (3–6)","bofm/2-ne/30.5"],"; ",["D&C 28:8 (8–9, 14)","dc-testament/dc/28.8"],"; ",["32:2","dc-testament/dc/32.2"],"; ",["49:24","dc-testament/dc/49.24"],"."]]]," might come to the knowledge of their fathers, and that they might know the ",["promises",["study-note-ref","b",[["2 Ne. 10:9 (9, 21)","bofm/2-ne/10.9"],"; ",["Alma 9:24","bofm/alma/9.24"],"."]]]," of the Lord, and that they may ",["believe",["study-note-ref","c",[["Morm. 3:21","bofm/morm/3.21"],"."]]]," the gospel and ",["rely",["study-note-ref","d",[["2 Ne. 31:19","bofm/2-ne/31.19"],"; ",["Moro. 6:4","bofm/moro/6.4"],"."]]]," upon the merits of Jesus Christ, and be ",["glorified",["study-note-ref","e",[["Moro. 7:26 (26, 38)","bofm/moro/7.26"],"."]]]," through faith in his name, and that through their repentance they might be saved. Amen."]]],"volume":"dc"}